verbose_text: Heatmap and violin plots revealed a high and overall unimodal expression of cell-cycle genes Mki67, Cdk4, Mcm6, Ccnd3, and Pcna, suggesting that the higher hematopoietic potential of the E7.5 ETV2 + FLK1 + cells was not due to increased proliferation.
evidence: expression of cell-cycle genes Mki67, Cdk4
